Tame Beast I Finish
    Events
        Unit - A unit Finishes casting an ability
    Conditions
        And - All (Conditions) are true
            Conditions
                (Ability being cast) Equal to Tame Beast I
                TM_TimerFinished Equal to True
    Actions
        -------- Locals --------
        Custom script:   local boolean registered
        -------- ================= --------
        Set VariableSet TM_Value = (Custom value of (Triggering unit))
        Set VariableSet Pet_TamerChanneling[TM_Value] = False
        Unit - Change ownership of UDexUnits[TM_Value] to Player 19 (Mint) and Retain color
        -------- UNIT HIDER --------
        Set VariableSet UnitHider_ReferenceUnits[(Custom value of UDexUnits[TM_Value])] = UDexUnits[TM_Value]
        Unit Group - Add UDexUnits[TM_Value] to UnitHider_ReferenceGroup
        -------- ============  --------
        Sound - Play Rescue <gen>
        Game - Display to (All players) the text: (Name of UDexUnits[TM_Value])
        Game - Display to (All players) the text: (Pets:  + ((String((Number of units in TamedUnits))) +  / 1))
        -------- Player can have only 1 tamed beast at a time --------
        Unit Group - Add UDexUnits[TM_Value] to TamedUnits
        Unit - Add Inventory (Hero) to UDexUnits[TM_Value]
        Unit - Make TamedUnit Vulnerable
        -------- Decide what focus group --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                Pet_Tamer[TM_Value] Equal to Nazgrek
            Then - Actions
                Unit Group - Add UDexUnits[TM_Value] to CompanionFocusNazgrek
            Else - Actions
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                Pet_Tamer[TM_Value] Equal to Zulkis
            Then - Actions
                Unit Group - Add UDexUnits[TM_Value] to CompanionFocusZulkis
            Else - Actions
        -------- Add to multiboard --------
        Set VariableSet TamedUnit = UDexUnits[TM_Value]
        -------- xp --------
        Custom script:   set registered = UnitExperience_IsUnitRegistered(udg_TamedUnit)
        Custom script:   if registered != true then
        -------- Register to XP system --------
        Custom script:   call UnitExperience_RegisterUnit(udg_TamedUnit)
        Custom script:   else
        -------- Unit already registered by XP system - just re-enable XP --------
        Custom script:   call UnitExperience_DisableXP(udg_TamedUnit, false)
        Custom script:   endif
        Set VariableSet Pet_Dead = False
        -------- Reset values --------
        Set VariableSet TamedUnitKillCount = 0
        Set VariableSet TamedUnitDeathCount = 0
        Trigger - Run MultiboardUpdate Add Tamed <gen> (checking conditions)
